  et al. 2000
 ; 
 Fletcher 
  et al. 2001
 ; 
 McGraw and Furedi 2005; 
 Wiegmann and Waller 2006; 
 Wang and Mopper 2008; 
 Knight 
  et al. 2009a
 ; 
 Frerker 
  et al. 2014
 ).
